room_title: Escape room "The Cellar" by Escape Chambers in Des Moines
room_description:
“Where… where am I?...” The last thing you remember was the bar and if there’s one thing you know, this ain’t it. Bodies strung from the ceiling, a horrible stench wafting through the air… If you want to make it out alive, panicking is not an option.
Participants may be physically restrained.
